title: Glenn Beck 2011-12-27 (incl. 4th hour) CF mp3 48K
description:
This torrent includes the official podcast mp3s released on the www.glennbeck.com website for the radio show. It includes the "4th Hour" with Pat & Stu which is available only to subscribers (ie. it is not part of the regular radio broadcast).

Sorry these are late again, I'm out of the country, and very busy. I'm sure everyone isn't that worried since these are all guest-hosts, but I still feel badly that I'm not getting the podcasts up as usual.

Tuesday has Mike Broomhead filling in for Glenn who is on holidays.
